            "name": "38d207ed",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "<span style=\"font-size:18px\">This dashboard tracks monthly accommodation prices across Tokyo and Osaka for 2024, based on confirmed booking data. Prices tend to peak during spring (March–April, cherry blossom season) and at the end of the year. The most affordable months for travel are January and June. Tourist agencies looking to organise budget-friendly trips to both cities should target these off-peak windows, where combined nightly rates are lowest. Hosts and property owners can use the same data to set premium pricing in high-demand months and lower prices in the quieter periods.</span>"
              ]
